N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 153.10 - Group insurance producers

State Regulations

No person shall act as an insurance agent or broker in regard to any group or quasi-group program, unless duly licensed under article 21 of the Insurance Law, consistent with section
5911 (c)
of the Insurance Law in connection with a federal purchasing group. Notes
